               feloniously stealing one pair of linen sheets, value 8 s. in the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17811205-12-victim167" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Cuthbert
                        <interp inst="t17811205-12-victim167" type="surname" value="Cuthbert"></interp>
